            <title>[LU-5437] In the lustre client 2.5.2 mounted folder has wrong last modify time, is in the future 2106.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5437</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I do stat on /lustre mount point I get wrong time:&lt;br/&gt;
 stat /lustre&lt;br/&gt;
  File: `/lustre&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
  Size: 4096            Blocks: 8          IO Block: 4096   directory&lt;br/&gt;
Device: b1f34764h/2985510756d   Inode: 144115188193296385  Links: 30&lt;br/&gt;
Access: (0755/drwxr-xr-x)  Uid: (    0/    root)   Gid: (    0/    root)&lt;br/&gt;
Access: 2014-06-06 00:23:46.000000000 +0200&lt;br/&gt;
Modify: 2106-02-16 14:24:47.000000000 +0100&lt;br/&gt;
Change: 2106-02-16 14:24:47.000000000 +0100&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If lustre is not mounted the time is correct:&lt;br/&gt;
 stat /lustre/&lt;br/&gt;
  File: `/lustre/&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
  Size: 4096            Blocks: 8          IO Block: 4096   directory&lt;br/&gt;
